'''三硝基胺'''是一种[[氮氧化物|氮氧化物]]，化学式为N(NO<sub>2</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。这种化合物在2010年由瑞典[[皇家工学院|皇家工学院]]的研究者发现。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/anie.201007047/abstract |title=Angewandte Chemie International Edition, Early View,  Dec. 23, 2010 |accessdate=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2011-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020085906/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/anie.201007047/abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此前曾{{who|有人}}猜测存在三硝基胺。{{来源请求}}<!-- it is not clear that this assertion is supported by the end-of-paragraph cite of Montgomery and Michels, 1993.  Can we have a short quotation added to the citation, please? --> 蒙哥马利和米歇尔斯1993年进行的理论计算表明该物质是稳定的。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Structure and stability of trinitramide |author=J. A. Montgomery Jr. and H. H. Michels |journal=[[Journal_of_Physical_Chemistry|Journal of Physical Chemistry]] |volume= 97 |issue=26 |pages=6774–6775 |date=July 1993 |accessdate=December 22, 2010 |doi=10.1021/j100128a005}}</ref>

三硝基胺在未来可能用作最有效和污染最小的[[火箭推进剂|火箭推进剂]]氧化剂，因为它不含氯。<ref name=sd20101222>[http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/12/101222071831.htm Discovery of New Molecule Could Lead to More Efficient Rocket Fuel] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/12/101222071831.htm |date=20111014034328 }}, ''[[Science_Daily|Science Daily]]'', 2010-12-22, accessed 2011-01-03.</ref>
这是一项可能重大的发现，因为根据[[齐奥尔科夫斯基火箭方程|齐奥尔科夫斯基火箭方程]]，即使火箭的[[ΔV|ΔV]]改进很小，也能大大增加火箭的有效载荷。
它的能量密度比现有最高的也要高出20-30%，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/News/2011/January/07011103.asp |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2011-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110129180716/http://www.rsc.org/chemistryworld/News/2011/January/07011103.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是其他燃料与液氧混合能量密度会更高。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/store/10.1002/anie.201007047/asset/supinfo/anie_201007047_sm_miscellaneous_information.pdf?v=1&s=2b7789919ea7a0858400749fd4a8859942236a1e |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026091336/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/store/10.1002/anie.201007047/asset/supinfo/anie_201007047_sm_miscellaneous_information.pdf?v=1&s=2b7789919ea7a0858400749fd4a8859942236a1e |archive-date=2012-10-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

